  {% include 'posts/_include/_inner-universe-vocabulary-5.njk' %}
  <h3>6. <span class="russian">Бесконечный бег…</span></h3>
  {% include 'posts/_include/_inner-universe-vocabulary-6.njk' %}
  <h3>7. <span class="russian">Пока жива я могу стараться на лету не упасть,</span></h3>
  {% include 'posts/_include/_inner-universe-vocabulary-7.njk' %}
  <h3>8. <span class="russian">Не разучиться мечтать… любить…</span></h3>
